OL,3,CSwinney optimistic Government can
OL,4,C'greatly enhance' lives despite budget
OL,5,Cwoes
OL,7,FThe Scottish Government remains
OL,8,F"optimistic" it can still "enhance the
OL,9,Flives of children and their families",
OL,10,Fthe First Minister has said ahead of
OL,11,Fhis first Programme for Government.
OL,13,FJohn Swinney will set out his
OL,14,Flegislative plans for the next 12
OL,15,Fmonths in Holyrood on Wednesday, just
OL,16,F24 hours after his Finance Secretary
OL,17,Flaid out the stark financial picture
OL,18,Ffacing the country.
