OL,3,CSwinney optimistic Government can
OL,4,C'greatly enhance' lives despite budget
OL,5,Cwoes
OL,7,FShona Robison announced #500 million
OL,8,Fin savings on Tuesday, including #188
OL,9,Fmillion to be found across Government,
OL,10,Fincluding by cutting active travel
OL,11,Ffunding, #65 million by repurposing
OL,12,Fcash from other projects and around
OL,13,F#60 million through already announced
OL,14,Fspending controls.
OL,16,FUp to #460 million from the ScotWind
OL,17,Fleasing round will also be used, Ms
OL,18,FRobison said, in the hopes it will not
OL,19,Fall be required to be spent.
