OL,7,FThe "single greatest priority", the
OL,8,FFirst Minister has said, is to
OL,9,Feradicate child poverty and he has
OL,10,Fhinted at greater family support being
OL,11,Fdeployed as a result.
OL,13,F"No one's opportunities should be
OL,14,Fdetermined by the circumstances they
OL,15,Fare born into, which is why this
OL,16,Fyear's programme for government will
OL,17,Fprioritise measures focused on our
OL,18,Fsingle greatest priority of
OL,19,Feradicating child poverty.
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@^O]uD@AOU
