OL,3,CSwinney optimistic Government can
OL,4,C'greatly enhance' lives despite budget
OL,5,Cwoes
OL,7,F"To do this, we will support the whole
OL,8,Ffamily in ensuring they can access the
OL,9,Fhelp they need, when they need it.
OL,11,F"We already have a strong track record
OL,12,Fof improving the lives of children
OL,13,Facross Scotland, including through our
OL,14,Fgame-changing Scottish Child Payment
OL,15,Fand expansion of early learning and
OL,16,Fchildcare.
OL,18,F"This Government's policies are
OL,19,Festimated to keep 100,000 children out
OL,20,Fof relative poverty this year."
