OL,5,Cwoes
OL,7,FHe added: "These provide strong
OL,8,Ffoundations for this year's programme
OL,9,Ffor government, but we are determined
OL,10,Fto go further.
OL,12,F"Even as we face unprecedented
OL,13,Fbudgetary constraint, I am optimistic
OL,14,Fthat we can still greatly enhance the
OL,15,Flives of children and their families."
OL,17,FSince taking over from Humza Yousaf
OL,18,Fearlier this year, Mr Swinney
OL,19,Fpinpointed the end of child poverty as
OL,20,Fone of his key targets in office.
