OL,7,FRecent figures show the proportion of
OL,8,Fchildren living in relative poverty
OL,9,Fhas remained stubbornly high in recent
OL,10,Fyears with the figure sitting at 26%
OL,11,Fin 2022-23, despite legal targets
OL,12,Faiming to reduce the figure to less
OL,13,Fthan 18% by this financial year and
OL,14,F10% in 2030-31.
