OL,5,Cwoes
OL,7,FWhile child poverty is the key driver
OL,8,Fof Mr Swinney's first programme for
OL,9,Fgovernment, the First Minister said
OL,10,F"investment in public services,
OL,11,Fgrowing our economy and tackling
OL,12,Fclimate change all contribute to
OL,13,Fimproving lives and livelihoods" would
OL,14,Falso feature.
OL,16,FBut Scottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,17,Fsaid the Scottish Government had "lost
OL,18,Fits way", ahead of the statement.
