OL,3,CSwinney optimistic Government can
OL,4,C'greatly enhance' lives despite budget
OL,5,Cwoes
OL,7,F"Time and time again the SNP has
OL,8,Fripped up its flagship pledges and
OL,9,Fmissed its own targets, leaving every
OL,10,Finstitution in Scotland weaker," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"NHS waiting lists are at a record
OL,14,Fhigh, the attainment gap is widening
OL,15,Fin our schools, our justice system is
OL,16,Fat breaking point and SNP financial
OL,17,Fchaos means more cuts are looming.
OL,19,F"This is a government that has grown
OL,20,Fout of touch and run out of ideas."
