OL,4,C'greatly enhance' lives despite budget
OL,5,Cwoes
OL,7,FWith one eye on 2026, the Scottish
OL,8,FLabour leader said his party was "at
OL,9,Fwork to fix the carnage left behind by
OL,10,Fthe Tories", adding "but we need
OL,11,Fchange here in Scotland too".
OL,13,F"We need an end to 17 years of broken
OL,14,FSNP promises and a return to the
OL,15,Fpolitics of hope," he said.
OL,17,F"Scotland's best days do lie ahead of
OL,18,Fus but only Scottish Labour can
OL,19,Fdeliver the change our country so
OL,20,Fdesperately needs."
