OL,7,FThe Scottish Greens urged the First
OL,8,FMinister to focus on "human rights and
OL,9,Fequality" with the introduction of a
OL,10,FScottish human rights Bill and a ban
OL,11,Fon conversion therapy.
OL,13,F"These are crucial bills, and they
OL,14,Fhave been continuously delayed," said
OL,15,Fthe party's equality spokeswoman,
OL,16,FMaggie Chapman.
