OL,5,Cwoes
OL,7,F"Many of us want to see them
OL,8,Fintroduced with enough time for
OL,9,Fscrutiny, so that we can ensure they
OL,10,Fare as strong and as robust as
OL,11,Fpossible."
OL,13,FScottish Greens co-leader Lorna Slater
OL,14,Fsaid Mr Swinney's Programme for
OL,15,FGovernment is his last effort to save
OL,16,Fthe SNP's climate credentials, and
OL,17,Fthat the party is "rolling back on
OL,18,Fclimate action".
