OL,5,Cwoes
OL,7,FShe added: "With global temperatures
OL,8,Frising, we urgently need bold and
OL,9,Fambitious change.
OL,11,F"We have no time to waste, but the SNP
OL,12,Fis taking us backwards and undermining
OL,13,Fa lot of the progress that was
OL,14,Fintroduced by the Scottish Greens.
OL,16,F"Our focus must now be on urgently and
OL,17,Frapidly delivering the policies that
OL,18,Fwill help us to cut our emissions and
OL,19,Fseize the immense potential of our
OL,20,Fgreen transition."
